&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;As an&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Area Vice President&lt;/strong&gt;, you will develop and execute sales plans, lead conversations and build deep relationships with health system executives, and manage the sales process from start to finish while helping to shape the future of our go-to-market approach.&lt;/p&gt;
