&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Full Stack Engineer,&lt;/strong&gt; you will play a pivotal role in redefining healthcare operations by developing highly scalable systems and algorithms, contributing to our mission of simplifying how healthcare operates rapidly in an AI First environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement full-stack systems that are reliable enough to delight care teams in a healthcare setting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a deep understanding of the solution area you’re working in and solve modern healthcare solutions collaboratively with the product team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up-to-date on modern security design principles, threats &amp;amp; preventive implementations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Learn new technologies and work effectively in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work collaboratively and learn together with the rest of the team members - a rising tide raises all boats.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BS, MS or PhD in Computer Science or equivalent work experience of 4+ years.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;4+ years of professional experience as a software engineer working full stack with Python and Typescript / React.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Amazon Web Services or other cloud services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;An AI Coding evangelist that measures themselves by the number of coding agents they’re orchestrating at once.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bonus Points For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Kubernetes (Strongly desired)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have worked in healthcare tech, especially Smart on FHIR, CDS and other EHR integrations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience working for an enterprise SaaS company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Candidates must be located in Brazil, Mexico, Colombia, Argentina, Peru, Chile, Guatemala, Ecuador, Bolivia, Dominican Republic, Honduras, Paraguay, El Salvador, Costa Rica, or Uruguay.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
