&lt;p&gt;The&lt;strong&gt; Senior Client Success Partner &lt;/strong&gt;will play a key role in ensuring successful deployment and adoption of Qventus&#39; perioperative and PCC solutions. They will develop deep relationships with key leaders and users in hospitals, acting as a critical link between Qventus and the client, and our internal delivery and product teams.&lt;/p&gt;
