&lt;li&gt;Convert early market interest into signed agreements and measurable revenue with urgency and accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead the Commercial Go-to-Market&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
