&lt;li&gt;Identify, engage, and close net-new health system logos while driving expansion revenue within the existing customer base&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and own relationships with economic buyers — CFOs, CMOs, CDI and Revenue Cycle leaders — who control budget and approval&lt;/li&gt;
